<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 14:06:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>OSINT显示美国第三支海军部队抵达中东，各国准备撤离数千人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/osint-third-u-s-naval-group-arrives-in-mideast-countries-prep-to-evacuate-thousands/0000018b-854f-d805-a98f-b5df147e0000</link><description>埃及附近的一支舰队部署了 2,000 名美国海军陆战队员，艾森豪威尔号航空母舰已经在克里特岛以西，战斗机和加油机已驻扎在海湾，数十架飞机和特种部队部署在塞浦路斯，以防突发事件。以色列、真主党和伊朗之间</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 13:02:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/osint-third-u-s-naval-group-arrives-in-mideast-countries-prep-to-evacuate-thousands/0000018b-854f-d805-a98f-b5df147e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的阿拉伯公民面临残酷的困境：我们的国家正在与我们自己的人民作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/arab-citizens-of-israel-face-a-cruel-quandary-our-state-is-fighting-our-own-people/0000018b-83ea-df47-a3df-ffeba6a60000</link><description>这场战争使我们以色列的阿拉伯公民陷入了前所未有的、不可能的境地，夹在哈马斯和警察麦卡锡主义之间，哈马斯的残暴使我们失去了家人，而当我们表达对巴勒斯坦人表示同情的权利时，对加沙的不成比例的轰炸和警察麦卡锡主义人们</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 12:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/arab-citizens-of-israel-face-a-cruel-quandary-our-state-is-fighting-our-own-people/0000018b-83ea-df47-a3df-ffeba6a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在三周战争后庆祝被俘士兵回国，这是难得的幸福时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/bibi-king-of-israel-rings-out-in-israels-streets-as-captured-soldier-returns-home/0000018b-856e-d805-a98f-b5ff62de0000</link><description>奥里·梅吉迪什从哈马斯的囚禁中获救后返回加特村的家，场面欢乐，但也遇到了一些争议</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 12:37:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/bibi-king-of-israel-rings-out-in-israels-streets-as-captured-soldier-returns-home/0000018b-856e-d805-a98f-b5ff62de0000</guid></item><item><title>西方的战后计划是巴勒斯坦权力机构的生命线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/the-wests-post-war-plans-are-a-lifeline-to-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-8546-dd28-a7df-9557396f0000</link><description>法国、华盛顿甚至耶路撒冷的想法都认为巴勒斯坦权力机构是拯救以色列免于直接控制加沙地带的唯一希望</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 11:29:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/the-wests-post-war-plans-are-a-lifeline-to-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-8546-dd28-a7df-9557396f0000</guid></item><item><title>我也是大屠杀的幸存者。这就是现在需要做的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/i-too-am-a-survivor-of-a-massacre-this-is-what-needs-to-be-done-now/0000018b-8538-d055-afbf-b7bba2180000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 11:01:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/i-too-am-a-survivor-of-a-massacre-this-is-what-needs-to-be-done-now/0000018b-8538-d055-afbf-b7bba2180000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙南部去世：“我想回家。”至少喝淡水后我会死”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dying-in-southern-gaza-i-want-to-go-home-at-least-ill-die-after-drinking-fresh-water/0000018b-8526-d805-a98f-b5ffd9fc0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-31/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dying-in-southern-gaza-i-want-to-go-home-at-least-ill-die-after-drinking-fresh-water/0000018b-8526-d805-a98f-b5ffd9fc0000</guid></item><item><title>被困在达吉斯坦暴徒中的乘客：“我发送了语音备忘录告诉我的丈夫我爱他”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/passenger-trapped-in-dagestan-mob-i-sent-a-voice-memo-telling-my-husband-i-love-him/0000018b-84d7-d805-a98f-b4dfd7800000</link><description>以色列乘客在俄罗斯南部穆斯林占主导地位的地区首府马哈奇卡拉降落，在机场遭到愤怒的暴徒袭击。乘客的证词描述了他们的苦难经历</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/passenger-trapped-in-dagestan-mob-i-sent-a-voice-memo-telling-my-husband-i-love-him/0000018b-84d7-d805-a98f-b4dfd7800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的“第二次独立战争”将走向何方？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/where-will-netanyahus-second-war-of-independence-lead/0000018b-8169-df47-a3df-ff69e1790000</link><description>1948 年的创伤并没有被抹去，犹太人和阿拉伯人的叙述发生了冲突。总理试图向人们灌输一种生存斗争的意识，为伤害以色列的阿拉伯公民辩护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/where-will-netanyahus-second-war-of-independence-lead/0000018b-8169-df47-a3df-ff69e1790000</guid></item><item><title>一名以色列艺术家因《亲爱的哈马斯》而受到追捕，展示了生活模仿艺术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-hounding-of-an-israeli-artist-for-dear-hamas-shows-life-imitating-art/0000018b-80d1-dc95-a38f-fcf53e9a0000</link><description>在她的短视频中，Tamy Ben-Tor 达到了新的高度。这是一件艺术品，而不是一位艺术家亲眼所见的精品政治作品</description><pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:23:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-hounding-of-an-israeli-artist-for-dear-hamas-shows-life-imitating-art/0000018b-80d1-dc95-a38f-fcf53e9a0000</guid></item><item><title>外交部高级官员抨击以色列驻联合国特使佩戴黄星勋章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-31/ty-article/.premium/yad-vashem-chairman-slams-israels-un-envoy-for-donning-yellow-star/0000018b-849e-df47-a3df-fe9ffa010000</link><description>以色列联合国特使吉拉德·埃尔丹周一猛烈抨击安理会未能谴责